      "anchor_id": "issue-gothrumedia-gothru-maps-backend-go-33",
      "display_title": "Issue #33: Update API Get Photographers",
      "main_description_html": "<h2 dir=\"auto\">RESULT 18/06/26</h2>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">✅ Implementation Complete — Ready for Unit Testing</h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Add new value for status, can add search by multiple value.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Example Implementation :</p>\n<div class=\"snippet-clipboard-content notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"GET /v1/photographers/users/dashboard?filter=status&amp;search=1,3\"><pre class=\"notranslate\"><code class=\"notranslate\">GET /v1/photographers/users/dashboard?filter=status&amp;search=1,3\n</code></pre></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Implementation :</p>\n<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"images/image-d723cc0f-3ee0-41a1-8e4e-2f1bc6eff8ae.png\"><img width=\"1614\" height=\"609\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"images/image-d723cc0f-3ee0-41a1-8e4e-2f1bc6eff8ae.png\" style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto; max-height: 609px;; aspect-ratio: 1614 / 609; background-color: var(--bgColor-muted); border-radius: 6px\" class=\"js-gh-image-fallback\"></a>\n<hr>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Description</h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Update the <strong>filter logic so <code class=\"notranslate\">status</code> can be multiple</strong> on the photographers dashboard list endpoint.</p>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Caller (PHP) passes the params straight through:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-text-html-php notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"$url = env(&quot;BASE_URL_PHOTOGRAPHER&quot;) . &quot;/v1/photographers/users/dashboard&quot;;\n$params = [\n    'search' =&gt; $search,\n    'filter' =&gt; $filter,\n    'size'   =&gt; $size,\n    'page'   =&gt; $page,\n];\"><pre class=\"notranslate\"><span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>url</span> = <span class=\"pl-en\">env</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\">\"<span class=\"pl-s\">BASE_URL_PHOTOGRAPHER</span>\"</span>) . <span class=\"pl-s\">\"<span class=\"pl-s\">/v1/photographers/users/dashboard</span>\"</span>;\n<span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>params</span> = [\n    <span class=\"pl-s\">'<span class=\"pl-s\">search</span>'</span> =&gt; <span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>search</span>,\n    <span class=\"pl-s\">'<span class=\"pl-s\">filter</span>'</span> =&gt; <span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>filter</span>,\n    <span class=\"pl-s\">'<span class=\"pl-s\">size</span>'</span>   =&gt; <span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>size</span>,\n    <span class=\"pl-s\">'<span class=\"pl-s\">page</span>'</span>   =&gt; <span class=\"pl-s1\"><span class=\"pl-c1\">$</span>page</span>,\n];</pre></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Endpoint:</p>\n<div class=\"snippet-clipboard-content notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"GET http://192.168.1.194:3008/v2/photographers/users?search=&amp;continentId=&amp;countryId=&amp;cityId=&amp;cursor=&amp;size=&amp;disablecache=\"><pre class=\"notranslate\"><code class=\"notranslate\">GET http://192.168.1.194:3008/v2/photographers/users?search=&amp;continentId=&amp;countryId=&amp;cityId=&amp;cursor=&amp;size=&amp;disablecache=\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Current behavior (to change)</h2>\n<p dir=\"auto\">In <code class=\"notranslate\">src/action/v1/photographers/getPhotographersDashboard.go</code>, <code class=\"notranslate\">filter=status</code> matches a <strong>single</strong> value only:</p>\n<div class=\"highlight highlight-source-go notranslate position-relative overflow-auto\" dir=\"auto\" data-snippet-clipboard-copy-content=\"case &quot;status&quot;:\n    if isNum {\n        query = query.Where(&quot;status = ?&quot;, searchNum)\n    } else {\n        query = query.Where(&quot;status = -1&quot;)\n    }\"><pre class=\"notranslate\"><span class=\"pl-s1\">case</span> <span class=\"pl-s\">\"status\"</span>:\n    <span class=\"pl-k\">if</span> <span class=\"pl-s1\">isNum</span> {\n        <span class=\"pl-s1\">query</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-s1\">query</span>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">Where</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\">\"status = ?\"</span>, <span class=\"pl-s1\">searchNum</span>)\n    } <span class=\"pl-k\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"pl-s1\">query</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-s1\">query</span>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">Where</span>(<span class=\"pl-s\">\"status = -1\"</span>)\n    }</pre></div>\n<p dir=\"auto\">So a user can filter by exactly one status (e.g. <code class=\"notranslate\">1 pending</code>) but not several at once.</p>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Proposed</h2>\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>Accept <strong>multiple status values</strong> for the status filter — e.g. comma-separated <code class=\"notranslate\">search</code> (<code class=\"notranslate\">search=1,3,4</code>) or repeated values — and build <code class=\"notranslate\">WHERE status IN (?)</code>.</li>\n<li>Apply the same multi-value handling in the <code class=\"notranslate\">filter=all</code> branch where status is matched.</li>\n<li>Ignore/validate non-numeric entries gracefully (no whole-table fallback).</li>\n<li>Keep <code class=\"notranslate\">search</code>, <code class=\"notranslate\">size</code>, <code class=\"notranslate\">page</code>, <code class=\"notranslate\">disablecache</code> behavior unchanged.</li>\n<li>Controller <code class=\"notranslate\">src/controllers/v1/photographers/getPhotographersDashboard.go</code> parses the multi-value input before calling the action.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 dir=\"auto\">Acceptance criteria</h2>\n<ul class=\"contains-task-list\">\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=\"task-list-item-checkbox\" aria-label=\"Incomplete task\"> <code class=\"notranslate\">filter=status</code> with multiple values returns photographers matching <strong>any</strong> of the given statuses (<code class=\"notranslate\">status IN (...)</code>).</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=\"task-list-item-checkbox\" aria-label=\"Incomplete task\"> Single-status filtering still works (backward compatible).</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=\"task-list-item-checkbox\" aria-label=\"Incomplete task\"> Non-numeric / empty status values are handled gracefully (no full-table leak).</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=\"task-list-item-checkbox\" aria-label=\"Incomplete task\"> <code class=\"notranslate\">pagination.pages</code> reflects the filtered result set (see related count bug in <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4577808791\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/gothru-maps-backend-go/issues/19\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/GoThruMedia/gothru-maps-backend-go/issues/19/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/gothru-maps-backend-go/issues/19\">#19</a>).</li>\n<li class=\"task-list-item\"><input type=\"checkbox\" id=\"\" disabled=\"\" class=\"task-list-item-checkbox\" aria-label=\"Incomplete task\"> Response shape unchanged.</li>\n</ul>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Relates to <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"4577808791\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/gothru-maps-backend-go/issues/19\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/GoThruMedia/gothru-maps-backend-go/issues/19/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/GoThruMedia/gothru-maps-backend-go/issues/19\">#19</a>.</p>",
